These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, drama, epic, fantasy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, october, march
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, trance, salsa, metal
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, aristoff, bongani
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 2. the person watching drama movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of trance##1
11. the fan of trance is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Movie-Genre    | epic   | drama       | horror | fantasy   |
| Birthday        | january    | march  | october      | september |
| Music-Genre         | metal      | trance | salsa         | dubstep   |
| Cigar   | blend | dunhill       | aristoff        | bongani   |

