.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, pineapple, nectarine, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, october, july
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lavender, turquise, black
House: gothic-revival, modern, art-deco, farmhouse
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person eating pineapple is the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the art-deco house is the person eating nectarine##1
4. the person eating apple is between the person who's birthday is in april and the gothic-revival house##2
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person who likes black is the farmhouse house##1
7. the person who likes red is on the far right##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Food           | pineapple | apple | peach | nectarine |
| Birthday   | may  | october | april         | july      |
| Color         | turquise      | lavender    | black         | red   |
| House     | gothic-revival         | modern    | farmhouse          | art-deco         |

