.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
House: craftsman, victorian, modern, palace
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, card-games, cooking, chess
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, apricot, lavender, mauve
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, van, skateboard, roller
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the modern house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the palace house is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person who likes white is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
 9. the palace house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
10. the victorian house is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| House          | victorian | palace  | craftsman | modern      |
| Hobby   | camping       | chess    | card-games      | cooking      |
| Color           | mauve     | white     | apricot         | lavender   |
| Transport         | skateboard | scooter | van     | roller |

