6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
8. the person who likes blue is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person traveling to marseilles##2
9. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Color           | green     | blue | emerald | orange |
