.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, april, september
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, mexican, pakistani
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, designer, teacher, architect
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, purple, light-blue, azure
 1. the architect is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the malaysian is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who likes azure is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the teacher##1
 6. the mexican is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the mexican is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 9. the person who likes azure is the architect##1
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the designer##3
11. the pakistani is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Birthday         | january      | september | april       | october   |
| Nationality   | pakistani     | indonesian | mexican | malaysian |
| Job   | coach    | designer     | teacher        | architect       |
| Color     | light-blue | purple   | blood-red   | azure       |

