.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, boat, trike
4 different games are played: go, domino, canasta, backgammon
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, vegafina, ritmeester, havana
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, 7up, iced-tea, tea
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 4. the person playing domino is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking 7up##2
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 6. the baccarat-smoker is between the person playing domino and the person drinking coffee##2
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing backgammon##1
 8. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the boat is the person playing domino##1
10. the baccarat-smoker is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Transport          | skateboard | trike   | boat   | snowmobile |
| Game           | go   | canasta     | domino   | backgammon |
| Cigar   | vegafina    | baccarat    | havana   | ritmeester   |
| Beverage         | coffee    | 7up | tea | iced-tea    |

 